{"tid":1432253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"揾啲新嘢玩，你唔悶街坊, 觀眾都悶 (長文)","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T08:16:48.000Z","uid":282797,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f68a135f59afc79ca16ef3d2604eeb5f125bbb5","tid":1432253,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係P牌，我有嘢想講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不喜勿插 sor.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家發夢都發咗好耐，我哋係時候<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攪啲新嘢</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我哋唔悶，和理非，街坊都悶， <span style=\"color: red;\">香港人最怕悶</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />琴晚咁，玩吓觀星筆幾創新，又有noise<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔洗吓吓破壞，始終香港人都有潔癖，攪得多未必支持，又悶。<br />\n<br />\n另外，而家啲人話我哋發夢去攪啲狗，係夢境宣泄！<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋唔係齋宣泄</span></span>，我哋係想表達不滿！！！ 宣泄係唔理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我哋要話比人知我哋係理性，要用行為去表達，費事比人亂講，做新聞。最憎啲人亂講！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講吓我有咩建議，咩都試吓，唔好悶襯<br />\n<br />\n1. 首先，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">宣揚帶口罩</span></span>，將帶口罩成為潮流<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變成平常事，好似着3咁。冇事都可以帶，每日做，任何人都做，當口罩變成著3咁，帶口罩就唔再突出。其實帶口罩有好多好處，嗰啲唔關事嘅大媽，亞叔成日乜都影<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />帶口罩可以保護自己，特別係出活動時。帶口罩普遍咗，仲可以保護埋發夢嘅手足。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>帶口罩保護自己，保護別人。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋可以可以攪吓口罩日，甚至口罩月，變成普及。<br />\n<br />\n2. 全民零消費 / 不消費藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不消費藍店，呢個已經攪得唔錯，好多藍店真係少咗好多客，而家啲<span style=\"color: red;\">藍店都唔敢亂出聲支持正苦，驚冇生意</span>。我哋要繼續推，要令所有店知道支持我哋有幫襯，唔支持冇幫襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(呢個向藍絲學嘅)。<br />\n<br />\n紅底銀行更加要做嘢，佢哋大把<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑材料</strong></span>揾吓出嚟，人自然會走，或者去攞吓錢都好。黑材料唔一定要新嘅，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">舊聞都得</span></strong></span>，新定舊好少人睇得咁清楚，就算係舊又點，即係有發生過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細個有銀行傳唔掂，即滯提，香港人最驚冇錢。記得<span style=\"color: red;\">話比媽媽，姨媽，姑媽，婆婆，格離屋啲嬸嬸知</span>。但唔洗吓吓最大嗰間先，慢慢嚟，一定到佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 揾大陸舊聞炒番起佢，例如<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">毒奶粉，收村</span></span>等都係好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，等香港人記得大陸啲偉大事蹟。<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人善忘，等我哋幫佢回顧</span>！<br />\n<br />\n4. 攪吓<span style=\"color: red;\">真揾星夜</span>都唔錯，雖然想係香港觀星真係難過登月球 (多謝大財團，光污染)<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。越難揾，越要揾，唔洗吓吓狗房嘅，觀星咩地方都可以揾。自己諗吓咩地方啦。但真係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好騷擾街坊(認真，街坊咁好)，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我哋唔做狗行為</span></strong></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個有風險，小心使用！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">唔想狗偷懶</span>，去每區狗房投訴又得（不過要身份証，要小心），日日投訴唔同人，邊個hit，投訴邊個，邊區摧淚，投訴邊區。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定要有大人齊齊去</span></span>，唔係比佢哋玩番轉頭，佢哋蝦細路，只驚大人。記住要<span style=\"color: red;\">一人一個投訴</span> ，放工又可以做。有狗嘢號碼仲好！人<span style=\"color: red;\">哋以為我哋去開戰，我哋去投訴！玩轉party！</span><br />\n<br />\n暫時係諗到咁多，咩都試吓！要<span style=\"color: red;\">文武雙全</span>，武完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家文吓，用吓其他方法，要比<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">surprise</span>人，咁先好玩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人好怕悶，又怕攰，街坊個個咁大年紀唔支持得幾多次。吓吓攪到街坊受傷，我哋都唔過意得去。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417c30473ffc822d3b2ace2b2f248d9cdb895c7f","tid":1432253,"uid":141612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"清 睇你排板睇到眼花 推一推"},{"pid":"e69140cea78f19fd83ca3b93f03c9268756c9b41","tid":1432253,"uid":260783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:59:29.000Z","msg":"出部講過哂，係冇人做姐。"},{"pid":"cc12e6633a9eaa488baaa4ba87b8159227eed04f","tid":1432253,"uid":281584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"太空館真心減壓,有動力繼續戰鬥"},{"pid":"f2612c5d80de7ddb50d769ec7b8865f8c5d455ee","tid":1432253,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"罷買講左十世希望大家真係有用"},{"pid":"35ce0e366684bd0d827ab34f41429cfcf0cd8bb6","tid":1432253,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a9be211d33b93ab45fa96968856587399631f1","tid":1432253,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"1. 2. 3. 可自己做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847e6ed07554cc7f323dc1f2a1e6870073bfff16","tid":1432253,"uid":133743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2612c5d80de7ddb50d769ec7b8865f8c5d455ee","tid":1432253,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"罷買講左十世希望大家真係有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"罷買講左十世希望大家真係有<span style=\"color: red;\">做</span>"},{"pid":"d506db1c2500d14fbd3475d229b87a2a777b6d87","tid":1432253,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"847e6ed07554cc7f323dc1f2a1e6870073bfff16","tid":1432253,"uid":133743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2612c5d80de7ddb50d769ec7b8865f8c5d455ee","tid":1432253,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"罷買講左十世希望大家真係有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:03:59.000Z","msg":"罷買講左十世希望大家真係有<span style=\"color: red;\">做</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"做得好! 我都係，繼續!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8047f37ac0aba2cd07283866867d953e113c3ece","tid":1432253,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"417c30473ffc822d3b2ace2b2f248d9cdb895c7f","tid":1432253,"uid":141612,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"清 睇你排板睇到眼花 推一推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"接受意見，下次清啲! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fbbe24479c51b3c17925303612f45b8f39e283","tid":1432253,"uid":166541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40643005087f2bcba647a4b10492e794bc804787","tid":1432253,"uid":275976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"bcb98b5e018620ad6ec78ff080aafea438157e80","tid":1432253,"uid":282797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:16:03.000Z","msg":"【毒奶粉受害人被指敲詐】 【坐牢五年獲平反卻已家不成家】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/663606407164764/?v=663606407164764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F663606407164764%2F%3Fv%3D663606407164764&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO79qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=55ac3663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/663606407164764/?v=663606